        public static io.netty.buffer.ByteBuf convertJavaObjToAmf3(java.lang.Object msg)
                                                    throws java.io.IOException
        Convert Java Object to AMF3 protocol's byte[]
        参数:
        msg - Java object
        返回:
        return byte array see: ByteBuf.
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - amf3 output exception.
        java.lang.NullPointerException - where the msg is Null, throw the NullPointerException.
